    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Everted hemipenes of the holotype (IEBR 4326) of Opisthotropis voquyi sp. nov.: A) Sulcal view, and B) asulcal view of the fully everted left hemipenis. Photos:T.Ziegler." ;
