<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1156721>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Map of Vietnam showing the localities where the new series of Opisthotrophis jacobi was collected 1) Tam Dao, Vinh Phuc Province, 2) Sa Pa, Lao Cai Province, and 3) Tay Yen Tu Nature Reserve, Bac Giang Province, the type locality of Opisthotropis voquyi sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1156721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

